.RS 4

	
	
	  Returns TRUE if the type of the object matches
\fIpattern\&.\fR
Pattern evaluation is done using shell pattern matching\&. Types recognized include:
.sp
.it 1 an-trap
.nr an-no-space-flag 1
.nr an-break-flag 1
